  >
    There are several [anti-obesity drugs approved by FDA](https://www.niddk.nih.gov/health-information/weight-management/prescription-medications-treat-overweight-obesity) and nearly all of them target the brain except {Concepts.Orlistat Orlistat}, which reduces dietary fat absorption in the gut. {Concepts.Liraglutide Liraglutide} is considered as most effective weightloss drug. It increases post-meal insulin secretion.

